---
title: Herby Beef & Leek Shepherd's Pie  with Garlic Mash Topping
description: Let’s try our hand at the classic shepherd’s pie, filled with saucy beef and veggies like cosy leek. It’s a comfort dinner that
just gets comfier when a fluffy potato mash is spread on top to create the top of the pie. We’ve reached peak cosiness now!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/652916c5b776085eb7bd8b16-bde1f9a2.jpeg
